v0.5

  * Moved from local subversion repository to GitHub.

  * Rewritten to use the TeX Java Help Library (replacing
    JavaHelp and the Java Look and Feel Graphics Repository).

  * Updated to take into account GhostScript changes.

  * Removed fetch ICC function (target no longer available).

  * Added batch mode.

  * Changed to double hyphen long command line switches with single
    hyphen short switch abbreviations.

v0.4.1b:

  * Added -deletetmp and -nodeletetmp command line switches

  * Added missing message.downloading and message.unpacking labels

v0.4b:

  * Another attempt at fixing the paths when running on Windows.

  * getLabelWithValues now uses a StringBuilder instead of regex.

v0.3b:

  * Fixed paths when running on Windows. (Thanks to Paulo Cereda.)

v0.2b:

  * Added use ICC check box

  * Added licence dialog

  * Fixed reading title and author meta data

v0.1b:
  * Initial beta release
